Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which should I choose…Is this too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a rare chance\Nto go the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe I could take\Na small chance and…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…but it's embarrassing\Nto show my navel…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything\Nup top to show anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6} So, what are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please,  just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Lady Yoruichi, you're wonderful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, come on! Let me help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dashing, even when choosing swimwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no, no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to find\Nmy own swimwear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soi Fon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked out swimwear\Nfor you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,PINK LAMÉ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What…no way…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that's lame…too childish…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, wait a minute! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way Lady Yoruichi's\Nchoice would be wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…but am I okay with that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if she is Lady Yoruichi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there are times when\NI have to stand my ground!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lady Yoruichi! I think I'll\Ngo with this yellow one…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.04,0:01:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy her…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon is petite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she has a variety of\Nswimsuit styles to choose from…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing cute\Nin a larger size…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the perfect swimsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:42.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SEXY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute, Kiyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I can't wear that…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:55.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SEXY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided on this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's a good opportunity,\Nso choose that one, Isane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose that one, Isane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, m'am…forgive me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Women's Soul Reapers\NAssociation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has come to the World\Nof the Living for R&R!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And that's how it is" my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain\Nwhat happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pool that the Women's\NSoul Reapers Association
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had secretly been building in\Nthe Soul Society was destroyed…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scatter, Senbonzakura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh damn, he found it…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stingy Byakky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were discovered because{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you brazenly built it in\Nthe middle of the yard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time,\NI will fully equip it with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a device that will\Nintercept Captain Kuchiki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not the issue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…really,\Nwhat are we going to do now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Build it in a new location?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But where?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand the problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Call me "Executive Director" here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yes, sir…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have a good idea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, I do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a good opportunity for\Nall of us to go for R&R{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at a beach in\Nthe World of the Living.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– What?!\N– What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! The beach!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were\Nyou people thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that,\Nyou got to come to the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with all these\Nbathing-suit beauties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be thankful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, this is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should show your gratitude\Ntowards all the people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who've helped you\Nfrom day to day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you here, Byakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came because they\Nwanted to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for building a bathing place\Non my mansion grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please enjoy the World of\Nthe Living beach at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this constitute\Nas an apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now,\Ndon't think too hard, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all have a great time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake, you're all here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited Captain Ukitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be nice if he got\Nsome outside air once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:07:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here because Rangiku invited\Nus saying she prefers it lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had nothing to do, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been feeling better lately,\Nand this is a nice change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soaking in the rays of\Nthe summer sun feels great…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me…\NI suddenly felt dizzy…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you shouldn't\Nhave come, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should cool him down\Nwith some ice, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, go to that seaside kiosk\Nand bring back some ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you spare us some ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a racket, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado is here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you all…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Unohana\Nasked them to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers are my enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't say no\Nto Unohana's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We rented out\Nthe entire beach today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't spread\Nour wings as we'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the presence of people\Nfrom the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went though all that effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kurosaki, you were\Nsaying something about ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need it to\Ncool down Ukitake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who collapsed from\Ntoo much direct sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear! I'll get it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro! Ice, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I warned him\Nnot to over do it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiro! You're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you\Nwith everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having Toshiro\Nmake the ice we use here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at this seaside kiosk\Nwith Hyorinmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to use your Zanpakuto\Nfor something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.\NYou don't want the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry! Make us some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the Frosted Heavens!\NHyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make\Na test batch of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "curry mitsumame dasheen\Nfrappe" I thought up earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll share some\Nwith everyone later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That menu item…\Nsounds lethal…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake,\Nare you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to cause you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you all, I'm fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't force yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake, why did you\Ngather everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Inaugural\NBeach Arts Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Essentially, it's a contest about\Nbuilding various objects with sand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and choosing the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then,\Nplease break up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into groups of two or\Nthree people and begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the ocean,\Nbut we're playing with sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather break watermelons\Nor have a test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will receive\Na cash prize envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– We're on our way!\N– We're on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so about the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do,\NBig Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested\Nin the prize money,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not averse to\Nshowing off our artistic sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine just watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at\Nthis sort of thing, either…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Shihoin and\NSoi Fon aren't here either…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were\Ngoing to catch fish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went diving in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't come back since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think they're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two won't\Nhave any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a bucket somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to wet the sand first…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we press our breasts together\Nto create cleavage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can put water there\Nand carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, shall we give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your breasts like this and…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing\Nin broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breast buckets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's not\Neducationally proper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this,\Nso you're jealous, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were your breasts that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…welll…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanao has pads in her top!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, does that\Nlook done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next we need to see who\Nopens the castle gates first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in\Nsuch a childish contest…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Is that supposed to be\Nan excuse or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of losing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it! I'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was going to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ikkaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ikkaku-san buried alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig him out, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are a rowdy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't they work more quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, do not be concerned\Nwith what goes on around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on your own work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Forgive me, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay. Quite nicely done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I make\Nthe arms a little bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother is so talented!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a polished\Naesthetic sense…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, I still cannot\Nhold a candle to him…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:14:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the very least, I must try\Nmy very best not to hold him back…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may not be related,\Nbut they're two peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this heat, I'll collapse again\Nand cause everyone to worry…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Sentaro…\NI'm going to lie down a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake me when it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd put a flush toilet\Nin the seaside kiosk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyone! You're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing,\NKotsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm building a wall of sand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the sea breeze doesn't strike\Nthe captain while he's sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid…\NWhat're you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to block the sun's rays\Nbefore the sea breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go pick some flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gently block\Nthe sun's rays with flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll light incense
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the captain can\Nsleep more comfortably!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, this is a wonderful\Ncreation that appeals to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is a pretty bad joke…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Lunch service!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried noodles and rice balls
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,specially made by\Nthe seaside kiosk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have drinks, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…If you put it there…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of looks like\Na funerary offering…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, when you add all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake's team\Nwould appear to be the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Captain Ukitake\Nin the competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ikkaku! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Crab…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bury you bastards…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kotetsu!\NLieutenant Ise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vine is going\Ninside my swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my… That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take a photo, I could probably\Nsell it for a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an uncaring thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it appeared, after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unohana! What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was once rumored that\Na peculiar Hollow with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,immense Spiritual Pressure\Nappeared at this beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once rumored"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose a place\Nlike that for our R&R trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescuing Lieutenants Ise\Nand Kotetsu comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida! Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El Directo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritual Pressure attacks\Nare useless…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those vines have the power to\Nabsorb radiated Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't inflict damage by any\Nmeans other than a direct attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we have to slash it\Nwith a Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have my Substitute\NSoul Reaper Combat Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or any Gikongan right now,\Nso I can't become a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku! Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here on R&R.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had no reason to\Nbring our Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ichigo.\NI left Chappy at the seaside kiosk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured something\Nlike this might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I brought Zabimaru with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Zabi…ma…ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Byakuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Big Brother\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ukitake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect\Nthe captain at all cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do\Nsomething with just us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! Sado and I\Nwill take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, go and get your\NSubstitute Soul Reaper Combat Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill all enemy with your venom,\NSuzumebachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you waiting for?\NYou're being lax, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going after\Nsharks in the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Abarai dropped in\Nfrom above,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we became worried\Nand raced back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't wake up even once\Ndespite all this commotion…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that man all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You started the watermelon\Nbreaking already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watermelon breaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!\NIt tastes like watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally caught on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be the one to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a watermelon-breaking event
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,planned by Captains Kuchiki\Nand Ukitake and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that story earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a story I made up\Nto warm up the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special\Nwatermelon developed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Department of\NResearch and Development
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for use against Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she just say\Nan anti-Hollow watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What possible use could it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A day at the beach is synonymous\Nwith watermelon breaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked the acting\Nassistant chairwoman
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and had them bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it to your satisfaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a little surprise\Nfrom the captains?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy it, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to\Nenjoy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Icchi,\Nlet's eat some watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you can eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've prepared watermelon\Nfor everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,enjoy watermelon breaking\Nto your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the watermelon\Nbreaking game begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, Captain skipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,\NI can't stand the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all you men here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have no opinions\Nabout our swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't complimenting us\Nthe proper thing to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's asking too much of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying you'll say\Nsomething if we take them off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Nanao!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take it off\Nif that's what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You're drunk, aren't you?\N– Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's segment is about\NToshiro Hitsugaya's Hyorinmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the Frosted Heaven!\NHyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya's Hyorimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the most powerful of\Nthe ice and snow Zanpakuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and creates a giant dragon\Nof water and ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Bankai form is\NDaiguren Hyorinmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its power is immense,\Nbut it is a sad Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:24:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that ordinarily has no use\Nother than to make ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one\Nwho thinks that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,